      • getShowLogsInConsole

        public static boolean getShowLogsInConsole()
        Routes logging output to console. This option is not offered as a choice to a user via the preferences menu because this is supposed to be used by developers only. Change by means of settings file; false by default.
        Returns:
        true if logs should be displayed in console.

      • getSuppressLevel

        public static int getSuppressLevel()
        User preference indicating after how many of the same warning messages printing of that message should stop. Set at 5 messages by default, initialized by IDE (see SimpleIDE).
        If set to -1, warnings are always shown.
        Returns:
        current suppression level - max number of repetitions of same warning.
